#: /tmp/tmpt_qrfg9q.md:51
msgid "Afficher un Token sur une carte vectorial"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/tmpt_qrfg9q.md:52
msgid ""
"Pour afficher un `rtok` dans une carte vectorielle, il suffit de "
"glisser/déposer le fichier sur le plan.  Just drag and drop the rtok file "
"from your system file browser to the vectorial.\n"
"`rtok` does not work on old rolisteam maps."
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/tmpt_qrfg9q.md:54
msgid "Mettre à jour les points de vie"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/tmpt_qrfg9q.md:55
msgid ""
"When the rtok is loaded, it appears on the vectorial map and it is listed "
"inside the player/character list as a character of the localplayer (the "
"player who add them)."
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/tmpt_qrfg9q.md:57
msgid "L'initiative"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/tmpt_qrfg9q.md:58
msgid "![menu]({static}/images/tutonpcmaker/fr/menu_initiative.jpg)"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/tmpt_qrfg9q.md:60
msgid ""
"**Initiative** can be rolled from the vectorial map contextual menu.\n"
"When character has initiative score it appears on the left-top corner of "
"the token.\n"
"It is possible to unset the score (e.g at the end of the fight), or to hide "
"them (`menu > view > map > show/hide initiative`)"
msgstr ""

